sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    Title: Stage 1 — CI/CD Pipeline (Hetzner Only)

    actor DEV as 👨‍💻 Developer
    participant GH as GitHub
    participant REG as Docker Hub<br/>(or GHCR)
    participant RUNNER as GitHub<br/>Actions Runner
    participant K8S as K3s/Talos<br/>(Hetzner)
    participant APPS as Applications

    DEV->>GH: git push feature-branch
    GH->>GH: Pull Request opened
    DEV->>GH: Merge to main
    GH->>RUNNER: Trigger workflow

    RUNNER->>RUNNER: Run tests (pytest / jest)
    RUNNER->>RUNNER: lint + security scan
    RUNNER->>REG: docker build + docker push
    Note over RUNNER,REG: Image: api:v2.1.0

    RUNNER->>K8S: kubectl set image deployment/api
    RUNNER->>K8S: kubectl rollout status
    RUNNER->>K8S: helm upgrade --install api ./charts/api
    Note over RUNNER,K8S: Uses kubeconfig with Hetzner node IP

    K8S->>APPS: Rolling update pods
    K8S-->>DEV: ✅ Deploy notification

    rect rgba(0, 50, 100, 0.1)
        Note over RUNNER,K8S: Manual steps still required:
        - SSH into nodes for OS patches
        - Backup DB before migrations
        - Manually scale nodes via Hetzner Console
        - No auto-healing beyond K8s level
    end
